  "body": "Reproducible on Android:\r\n\r\n**Case 1:** Context menu appears while tapping below input fields area or on gallery/stickers buttons\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n1. Activate input field\r\n2. Tap on area below input field or on gallery/stickers buttons\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** context menu appears\r\n**Expected result:** context menu appears on tap inside active input field \r\n\r\nActual result: \r\n\r\n**Case 2:**  microphone permissions modal appears on tapping aside from audio message button area\r\n\r\n**Preconditions:** microphone permission is not granted yet\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n1. Tap on area aside from audio message button\r\n2. Observe the result\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** microphone permissions modal appears\r\n**Expected result:** context menu appears on tap inside active input field \r\n\r\nSee video below for both case 1 and 2 \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/235183288-91be4be3-332a-440d-bdba-26898f90a607.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
